    "For each criterion, we show the rating for the three educational levels individually.",
    "We average the results over faculties.",
    "The triangles mark the average ratings, the red horizontal bars mark the medians.",
    "The boxes span from the first to the third quartiles with black diamonds representing outliers.",
    "We identify four main findings from the aggregated results (Fig. 1): Firstly, ChatGPT receives, on average, higher scores for basic and scientific skills compared to the skills beyond scientific knowledge."
